\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Calibrated antenna temperature $T_A(\nu )$ for the SGP LO1420 combined spectrum, used as the Week-1 first system-check measurement in this report. No 21-cm HI emission line is detected, consistent with $b=-90^\circ $ ($N_{\rm  HI}\lesssim 1.7\times 10^{20}$\,cm$^{-2}$). The noise floor near $T_A\approx 30\,$K confirms the system calibration.}}{9}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
